superheroes.origin_description: A brilliant scientist exposed to gamma radiation during a bomb test, transforming him into a green-skinned monster when angry or stressed. The more angry he gets, the stronger he becomes.
superheroes.superpowers: Superhuman strength that increases with rage, near-invulnerability, regenerative healing factor, immunity to diseases, superhuman speed and leaping ability
